Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.48,0:00:12.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就没有什么能把高木同学吓得尖叫的办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.24,0:00:19.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,总之 像这样每天都被她捉弄的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.75,0:00:22.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:28.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.67,0:00:30.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.05,0:00:33.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.55,0:00:36.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:38.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没啊 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.10,0:00:41.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一起去学校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.69,0:00:44.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Comment: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:00.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,——op——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:19.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,比身高
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:24.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,被看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:26.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,刚才被她看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:29.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:30.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:33.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要一起骑车去学校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:34.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:37.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,被发现的话会挨骂的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:39.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你是不好意思才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:40.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:42.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:47.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看来我撞上电线杆的事情没被她看到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:54.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片也终于换长袖了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:58.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,最近变冷了 感觉差不多该换了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:01.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:04.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你长个了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:09.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,春天的时候感觉你的制服比现在宽松一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:10.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:16.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,现在有种「制服 is 正义」的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:20.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,难道我到发育期了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.51,0:03:27.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哎呀 最近一个劲地长个子 真难办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:29.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,难道到了发育期吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:33.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学倒是没感觉有什么变化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:40.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你这可是性骚扰哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:43.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,居然说没变化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:47.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:50.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我不是这个意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:54.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我说的是身高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:57.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我在说身高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:03:59.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你以为我在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:04.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:09.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:15.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感觉你还是没怎么长高
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:18.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不不不 长高了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:22.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,说不定我现在比高木同学还要高呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:27.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那来比比身高吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:35.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么要来这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.63,0:04:37.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,穿着鞋子比不出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:41.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,小心迟到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:43.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,马上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:44.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,来 背对背站好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:55.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.77,0:04:58.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感觉好暖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:04.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我说 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:10.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一般不都是轮流贴着墙壁作记号吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:12.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,两个人背对着量更准嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:20.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,应该差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:21.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:25.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,来嘛 西片也来确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:32.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:34.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我没说错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:37.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你没垫脚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:40.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 你居然怀疑我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:42.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:50.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,面对面的话 就算垫脚也会知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:55.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那个 那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:08.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感觉好像我要高一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:09.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因为我刚才垫脚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:13.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你果然垫脚了啊 大骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:16.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我可没有说过我没垫脚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:19.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太好了 终于赢过我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:24.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这个高木同学 一副从容的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:26.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,心里肯定很不甘心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:32.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,还有 我没有不甘心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:36.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因为要是块头变大的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.37,0:06:38.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就会撞上电线杆 很辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:50.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你看到了吗 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:51.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,走吧 去学校啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:53.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:57.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我说 高木同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:09.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:13.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有那么冷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:15.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉很怕冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:17.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:19.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,美奈 你手好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:28.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怕冷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.92,0:07:31.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:34.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,再这样干我可饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:40.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:44.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你们的手为什么那么冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:46.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:49.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,手冷的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:52.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,内心很温暖的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:56.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我觉得内心很温暖的人不会做刚才那种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.91,0:08:00.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好了好了 别那么记仇嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:05.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你再干的话我真的要生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:07.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你明明已经生气了好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:08.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:12.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等 不要啊早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:14.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这是心暖攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:17.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,救命啊 由加莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:22.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这是刚才的回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.86,0:08:27.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:30.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉的手 好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:33.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但她的心拔凉拔凉的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:35.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么会这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:37.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好冷啊 不要靠过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:39.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,心寒攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:40.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,走为上策
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:41.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:42.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:45.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:47.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:53.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你也可以摸回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:59.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}好冷啊好冷啊 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:00.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}不要逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:06.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我怎么可能会这样干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:13.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,都叫你住手了 好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:18.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,手冷的人 内心是暖的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:19.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哪里暖了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:25.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木和西片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.62,0:09:27.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天一起上学了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:29.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,关系真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:33.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,他们果然在交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:39.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:44.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片和高木在交往吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:45.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:47.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不在意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:49.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,他们关系特别好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:52.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉 你很羡慕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:54.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 因为嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:56.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,与其说是羡慕…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:10:02.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,美奈 由加莉说想和男生唧唧我我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:03.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我才没这样说过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:06.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,美奈 你在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:08.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,美奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:10.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的 早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:11.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不要突然跟我搭话啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:14.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,本来快要尿出来的 现在尿不出来了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:18.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早苗真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:21.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那个很有趣的 去看看比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.39,0:10:23.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的吗 我会看的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:23.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:32.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我想到了很厉害的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:34.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,如果是这个犀利的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:37.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,放学的时候肯定能捉弄到高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:43.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你在偷笑什么呢 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:47.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好猥琐喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:49.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我才没有想那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:51.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那种事情是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:52.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 都说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:54.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你脸好红
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:57.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可恶的高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:10:59.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,给我走着瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:01.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,话说回来 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.01,0:11:03.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:04.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:13.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不好 难道她发觉我在设计她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:17.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.19,0:11:19.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么你要再说一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:22.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:28.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,放学时你说不定还会改变主意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:31.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以的话到时候再给我答复吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:33.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.88,0:11:40.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她究竟怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:42.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,算了 反正不被发觉就行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:45.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:48.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天来我家玩超级大乱斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:48.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an7}原文スパプラ，应该是山寨明星大乱?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:49.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:54.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,抱歉 今天不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:56.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么啊 又要陪女朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:11:57.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,女朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:11:59.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是高木同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:02.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哈？你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:04.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,根本就不是那回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:06.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木和西片没在交往哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:10.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我刚才在厕所听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:11.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:12.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:15.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,突然想去小便了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.38,0:12:17.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,厕所…厕所…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:22.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那家伙刚才在厕所干什么去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:26.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,话说西片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:28.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,既然你们没在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:30.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那为什么你会和高木同学一起回家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.02,0:12:33.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这个嘛 因为被她邀请了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.39,0:12:36.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这不就是因为在交往吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:37.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:40.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,应该不是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:44.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:47.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,下节课要去实验室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:49.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不好 赶紧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:13:01.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 我觉得高木同学只是想捉弄我而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:06.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:09.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天不可以绕远路了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:14.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我想吃椪柑冰棍 我想吃椪柑冰棍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:16.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,大冷天的还吃什么冰棍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:18.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在被炉吃冰棍超棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:19.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:24.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「给我答复」也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:27.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要我重新邀请她的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:31.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感觉有点不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:35.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我还没邀请过她一起回家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.42,0:13:37.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.88,0:13:39.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:42.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太好了 高木同学来问我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:44.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我只要说个Yes就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:49.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天有人问我是不是在和西片交往
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:55.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,然后 我好像被认为是喜欢西片的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:14:00.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是不是因为总是我在邀请你一起回去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:04.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这个高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:06.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原来这就是你的目的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:09.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,创造出让我来邀请你的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:13.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,然后取笑我害羞的反应吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:16.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:18.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要强装平静
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:21.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「哼 这样啊」这样的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:25.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,诶 原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:26.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:31.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,话说回来 关于早上的答复
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:38.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,反正我没什么事 一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:43.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:45.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,加油啊我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:47.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只要跨过了这一关
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:50.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我就能捉弄到高木同学了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:57.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一起回家怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:04.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么办好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:09.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,开玩笑的 回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:12.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:18.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片好像还有什么计划的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:20.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,暴露了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:30.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,既然暴露了 那还是不要做比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:33.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但我好不容易想出来的点子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.07,0:15:38.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,话说我还完全没想过要怎样弄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:45.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要不要买果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:48.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感觉喉咙干干的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:53.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,大部分都卖完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:57.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明明想喝冷饮的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:15:59.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,剩下的只有…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:01.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,红豆汤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:03.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,还有猎奇的饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:03.65,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\fs120\pos(918,330)\frz3.238}艾草汁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:03.65,Takagisan-huamian-1,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\fs50\pos(1164,702)}西瓜味
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:05.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.94,0:16:08.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感觉无论选哪个都会后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:12.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,无论选哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:16.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要去别的自动贩卖机看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:21.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我喉咙也渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:23.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,总之先…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.71,0:16:32.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好难喝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:35.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看包装就能猜到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:38.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,钱白花了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:40.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:42.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样一来就能开始我的计划了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:45.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我说 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:52.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好喝的热饮和难喝得要命的饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.82,0:16:54.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哪个比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:02.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,二选一问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:08.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好喝但是烫手的饮料和难喝得要命的饮料吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:11.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么样啊高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:12.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,难以选择吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:14.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你就犯难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.17,0:17:17.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,让我看看你为难的表情 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:18.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.72,0:17:23.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是我喝了好喝的热饮发烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:25.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片会来探望我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:30.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这有什么关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:32.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,关系大着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:34.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不会来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:39.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,既然发烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:42.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我应该会去探望你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:45.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我选好喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:47.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:51.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦 真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:53.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这是什么感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:57.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学完全没有为难嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:18:02.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不如说为难的是我才对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:06.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,二选一问题的作战失败了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.73,0:18:09.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不不 放弃还为之过早
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:11.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那下一题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:12.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:16.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你是选一辈子没有零花钱呢 还是不再捉弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:18.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一辈子没有零花钱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.41,0:18:19.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:24.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因为我有压岁钱作积蓄 暂时没什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:27.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,到了高中只要打工就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:30.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以还是选捉弄西片比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:33.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我太小瞧高木同学了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:35.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,得问些更刁钻的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:37.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:40.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,从刚才开始你就在问些奇怪的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:44.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,难道说 你想让我为难吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:49.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没 没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:52.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我也要提问了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.77,0:18:58.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我不在和被我捉弄一辈子 哪个比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:01.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不在是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.37,0:19:03.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:09.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,虽然我也不想被她捉弄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:13.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但消失什么的…那也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:16.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那 我选被你捉弄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:21.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你果然喜欢被捉弄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:24.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才没有 肯定是讨厌被捉弄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:25.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.68,0:19:29.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不太希望你消失…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:32.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,也就是说 你想一辈子和我在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:35.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:37.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你脸好红哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.23,0:19:39.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可恶 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:42.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,让我发窘就这么有意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:45.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也得问个好问题才行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:46.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那么下一题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:48.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么 还要继续吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:54.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一辈子考零分 以及和我接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:55.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哪个比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.29,0:19:58.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,接…接…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:02.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哪个比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:06.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,考零分 看了书也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:08.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 无论干什么都是零分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:11.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:14.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样的话不仅以后肯定拿不到零花钱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.69,0:20:16.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,甚至连高中也上不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:20.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但要选了接吻的话 肯定会被她捉弄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.24,0:20:22.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你很纠结嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:24.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可恶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:27.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我越纠结 高木同学她就越开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:29.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,得赶紧作出选择
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:31.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,零分太残酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:33.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:35.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:37.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那 那就
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:39.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,选不是考零分那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:41.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是考零分的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:47.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,接 接吻的那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:55.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样啊 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.03,0:21:11.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 果然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:14.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片的个子要高一点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.58,0:21:17.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了西片
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:20.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我在比身高而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.35,0:21:36.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,到头来又被狠狠地捉弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:41.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是我学到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.23,0:21:43.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,其中一个选项一定要是选不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.94,0:21:46.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只要另一个是捉弄用的选项
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.20,0:21:48.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这场对决就能稳赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.45,0:21:50.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学 下一个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.99,0:21:52.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那么下一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:57.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,倒立着绕校园走一圈和两个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:21:59.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,稍微等一下 我不会倒立
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.96,0:22:02.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,话说还轮不到我提问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.80,0:22:04.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,首先要回答我的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.71,0:22:05.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 你看…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:50.53,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.61,0:00:54.95,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.95,0:01:05.25,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.71,0:01:14.09,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}校庭で君のことを一番に見つけて今日は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.13,0:01:22.35,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて話しかけようか？ ちょっと考えるの楽しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.39,0:01:25.31,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風に揺らされるカーテン
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.10,0:01:30.69,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不意打ちに当たる日差し
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.77,0:01:34.61,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}眩しそうな顔を笑ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.82,0:01:38.49,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}照れて伏せちゃうのね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.41,0:01:46.62,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}憂鬱なテストも吹き飛ばせるような
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:54.88,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ねえ、二人で秘密の約束をしたいなって提案です
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:02:00.30,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:04.31,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:14.57,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Comment: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPCH——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:50.53,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}会错意了也没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.61,0:00:54.95,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}和你一起就是幸福 这样想着却不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.95,0:01:05.25,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}弥漫在周围的那阵幽香 想在你的身边静静感受
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.71,0:01:14.09,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}在校园的庭院 第一个发现你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.13,0:01:22.35,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}今天要和你说些什么呢 即便是想着这些也是一种乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.39,0:01:25.31,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}窗帘随风起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.10,0:01:30.69,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不经意地投入一束阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.77,0:01:34.61,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你那美丽的容颜笑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.82,0:01:38.49,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}羞得我抬不起头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.41,0:01:46.62,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}风儿喧嚣 似要吹散考试的忧郁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:54.88,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}呐 我想要和你一起 立下两人的秘密约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:02:00.30,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}会错意了也没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:04.31,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}和你一起就是幸福 这样想着却不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:14.57,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}弥漫在周围的那阵幽香 想在你的身边静静感受
Comment: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,——EDJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.05,0:22:16.14,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}広い宇宙の数ある一つ　青い地球の広い世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.14,0:22:25.11,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}小さな恋の思いは届く　小さな島のあなたのもとへ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:31.16,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}あなたと出会い　時は流れる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.41,0:22:35.83,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}思いをこめた　手紙もふえる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.00,0:22:40.75,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}いつしか二人互いに響く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.79,0:22:45.46,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}時に激しく　時に切なく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.51,0:22:50.14,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}響くは遠く　遥か彼方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.14,0:22:54.89,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}優しい歌は　世界を変える
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.39,0:23:01.69,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ほら　あなたにとって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:07.69,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}大事な人ほど　すぐそばにいるの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.69,0:23:13.83,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ただあなたにだけ　届いて欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.87,0:23:17.20,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}響け恋の歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.20,0:23:26.17,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ほら　ほら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.34,0:23:35.22,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ほら　響け恋の歌
Comment: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,——EDCH——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.05,0:22:16.14,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}想把这辽阔宇宙中绝无仅有的小小的相思之情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.14,0:22:25.11,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}传达给蔚蓝地球上广阔世界中小小岛屿上的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:31.16,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}与你邂逅 光阴飞逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.41,0:22:35.83,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}饱含思念的信件堆积如山
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.00,0:22:40.75,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不知不觉我们心生共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.79,0:22:45.46,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}时而充满激情 时而伤感不已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.51,0:22:50.14,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}回响渐渐远去 到那遥远彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.14,0:22:54.89,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你那温柔的歌声 改变了我的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.39,0:23:01.69,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你看 对你而言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:07.69,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}重要的人近在咫尺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.69,0:23:13.83,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}只愿你能感受到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.87,0:23:17.20,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}这响彻天地的恋歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.20,0:23:26.17,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你听 你听
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.34,0:23:31.51,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}听见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.51,0:23:35.22,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}这响彻天地的恋歌
